In the past five years, no accidental chlorine gas releases have occurred at the Salem Water Treatment Plant.

An emergency response plan is established and coordinated with the City of Salem LEPC. The plan includes plant evacuation procedures, first responders' emergency notification procedures, and a general public notification plan.

